reviewText: I would really have loved to have the complete shows. As a high school student, I was in the on-camera audience of one of these episodes, with the Fifth Dimension, and that experience was a very special memory for me.

Enjoyable but disappointing.  These are edited episodes ( i assume for space). Would have been much better as a compilation with one set of credits instead (there's like 15 mins worth it seems). Most obvious edit is Dusty's medly is chopped in half :-(
